      "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/h/4491bb/{size}.png",
      "created_at": "2022-08-02T21:03:05.145Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Right on. The data nerd in me wants to get one just for that fact. I do mostly ride on my own and find myself racing against myself but I don\u2019t have a bar mounted computer or anything. I just compare based on the recording (using my watch).</p>\n<p>I also use a PMC chart to manage my fatigue as I\u2019ll get caught up in the numbers and trying to improve them only to not let myself recover\u2026</p>",
