    {
      "id": 7046,
      "name": "",
      "username": "htims05",
      "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/h/4491bb/{size}.png",
      "created_at": "2022-08-07T22:48:56.510Z",
      "cooked": "<p>So to day I put my assioma\u2019s on my mountain bike and went and did a route that I take regularly.  You get so much more info having power than you do if you just go ride.  That said the load for the ride with the power pedals is almost half that of what it estimates without it.  Now I don\u2019t know if that\u2019s because the last ride I was well fatigued compared to the ride with power - first ride after a week of vacation so maybe that plays into it as well - but my HR was pretty much the same.</p>\n<p>Without Power:<br>\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/original/2X/b/b3bd30a8ba55205ff39f5248681c4700d6648c86.png\" data-download-href=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/b3bd30a8ba55205ff39f5248681c4700d6648c86\" title=\"NoPower\"><img src=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/b/b3bd30a8ba55205ff39f5248681c4700d6648c86_2_690x242.png\" alt=\"NoPower\" data-base62-sha1=\"pE2NUI6aFT9j9mrsam93NyiBo6W\" width=\"690\" height=\"242\" srcset=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/b/b3bd30a8ba55205ff39f5248681c4700d6648c86_2_690x242.png, https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/b/b3bd30a8ba55205ff39f5248681c4700d6648c86_2_1035x363.png 1.5x, https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/b/b3bd30a8ba55205ff39f5248681c4700d6648c86_2_1380x484.png 2x\" data-small-upload=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/b/b3bd30a8ba55205ff39f5248681c4700d6648c86_2_10x10.png\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">NoPower</span><span class=\"informations\">1823\u00d7642 102 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>\n<p>With Power:<br>\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/original/2X/f/f64797137df0c0b43410ab4b5d71229da1c7b83e.png\" data-download-href=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/f64797137df0c0b43410ab4b5d71229da1c7b83e\" title=\"WithPower\"><img src=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/f/f64797137df0c0b43410ab4b5d71229da1c7b83e_2_690x313.png\" alt=\"WithPower\" data-base62-sha1=\"z8GQ0JukbeFsup2cmtdkBDYYPdc\" width=\"690\" height=\"313\" srcset=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/f/f64797137df0c0b43410ab4b5d71229da1c7b83e_2_690x313.png, https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/f/f64797137df0c0b43410ab4b5d71229da1c7b83e_2_1035x469.png 1.5x, https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/f/f64797137df0c0b43410ab4b5d71229da1c7b83e_2_1380x626.png 2x\" data-small-upload=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/f/f64797137df0c0b43410ab4b5d71229da1c7b83e_2_10x10.png\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">WithPower</span><span class=\"informations\">1823\u00d7828 201 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>",
