      "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/m/57b2e6/{size}.png",
      "created_at": "2022-08-08T09:18:43.960Z",
      "cooked": "<p>I forgot another nifty function in Intervals:<br>\nHave you tried using HRSS (normalized TRIMP) for HR load?<br>\nIf you have enough workouts with both Power and HR data, Intervals builds an algorithm in the background that will be used to calculate a HR load that is way better matching the Power load.<br>\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/original/2X/4/4d55d824a35c554697aced39d2e15e49edc494ba.png\" data-download-href=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/4d55d824a35c554697aced39d2e15e49edc494ba\" title=\"image\"><img src=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/4/4d55d824a35c554697aced39d2e15e49edc494ba_2_517x354.png\" alt=\"image\" data-base62-sha1=\"b28GwfmHvDt89pqEmIZUEPtfLNE\" width=\"517\" height=\"354\" srcset=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/4/4d55d824a35c554697aced39d2e15e49edc494ba_2_517x354.png, https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/4/4d55d824a35c554697aced39d2e15e49edc494ba_2_775x531.png 1.5x, https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/original/2X/4/4d55d824a35c554697aced39d2e15e49edc494ba.png 2x\" data-small-upload=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/4/4d55d824a35c554697aced39d2e15e49edc494ba_2_10x10.png\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">995\u00d7683 82.6 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>",
